      <p>Have questions about any of these? <a href="/support">Reach out on the support page</a> or <a href="https://github.com/numanaral/mermaid-toolkit-for-google-docs/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">open an issue on GitHub</a>.</p>
    </div>
